      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong>,<strong> chopped parsnips</strong> and <strong>halved Brussels sprouts</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and<strong> </strong>put the tray[s] in the oven for an initial 15-18 min or until the potatoes are tender</p>",
