    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>soft cheese</strong> to a measuring jug with your <strong>dried thyme</strong>,<strong> roasted garlic paste</strong>, <strong>Chinese rice wine </strong>and<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong></p><p>Mix until fully combined, then add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Stir it all together and set aside – this is your<strong> sauce</strong></p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
