      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are tender, add the<strong> halved Tenderstem </strong>and <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> to the tray[s]</p><p>Tip: Nestle the basa in between the vegetables!</p><p>Top each basa fillet with a small knob of<strong> butter </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong>, then return the tray[s] to the oven and cook for a final 12-15 min or until the fish is cooked through – this is your <strong>buttered basa</strong> <strong>& sprout tray bake</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
